@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here
@readingId = 1
@meterId = 1

### List all readings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/readings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Capture a meter reading (ROLE_OPERATOR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/readings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meterId": {{meterId}},
  "previousReading": 1240.0,
  "currentReading": 1285.5,
  "readingDate": "2026-06-05"
}

### Get a reading by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/readings/{{readingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List readings for a meter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/readings/meter/{{meterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}